  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nAs some people tend to set the %dev and %test properties directly in the applications.properties file it would be good to have an option to clean them out when doing a prod build.\r\n\r\nSo that  e.g.:\r\n%dev.quarkus.datasource.jdbc.url=jdbc:postgresql://dev-db:5654/myapp\r\n%dev.quarkus.datasource.username=test123\r\n%dev.quarkus.datasource.password=mys3cur3pw\r\n\r\nIs not in the final build anymore.\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\nProbably with:\r\n\r\n-Dquarkus.cleanup-properties=dev\r\n-Dquarkus.cleanup-properties=dev,test\r\n",
